             was indicted for <rs id="t18311201-43-off238" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18311201-43-off238" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18311201-43-off238" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18311201-43-cd239" type="crimeDate">27th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-43-off238 t18311201-43-cd239"></join>, 6 sovereigns
            </rs>, the monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t18311201-43-victim495" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     North
                  <interp inst="t18311201-43-victim495" type="surname" value="North"></interp>
